Author: Browsers Lab
Title: [ANN][BAL][PRE-ICO] Browsers Lab - Revolutionizing Software Automation
Body: WHITEPAPER | WEBSITE | TWITTER | FACEBOOK | TELEGRAM | YOUTUBE | MEDIUM   Browsers Lab Alpha Version   BROWSERS LAB Revolutionizing Software Automation Browsers Lab is a cloud-based test automation platform. Store and execute tests on different environments, browsers, and mobile devices. Selenium, Appium and JavaScript unit testing frameworks make Browsers Lab a comprehensive testing platform.   A solid service for the blockchain Browsers Lab's ambitious goal is to make cloud-based testing easier. A platform to reduce the expense associated with managing, creating and executing tests. Leveraging our platform will reduce the overall effort with setting up different environments, and viewing the results. Deliver with even greater confidence as our dashboard and metrics provide insight into how the tests are performing. Any team can benefit from our platform, small or large. From an individual to enterprise scale. Browsers Lab has your back.  Browsers Lab Token will help this platform grow and expand to fill the industries test automation needs. Regulated by smart contracts on an Ethereum based blockchain platform. Not only will the token help foster a much-needed platform, but will also create a new market. The Browsers Lab Token will facilitate individuals and companies by exchanging services in a secure manner.   Browsers Lab Basic Architectural model As Browsers Lab grows, so will our support for desktop and mobile applications. Browsers Lab will provide a desktop application (Windows, Mac, and Linux) to have the ability to code your tests directly from the OS of your choosing. Browsers Lab in addition to the desktop application will also provide applications for your Android and iOS devices.   Browsers Lab Token (BAL) Browsers Lab Token is regulated by smart contracts on an Ethereum based blockchain platform. Our versatile token will be used for multiple products and services offered by Browsers Lab. Using our token you will have the ability to hire freelancers, pay or reward your employees, use it on our platform for services, etc.  Etherscan Address: https://etherscan.io/address/0xA9d6a1c87422b211014f1009C541600b33344AFF#code   Software Automation Industry Analysis The software automation industry is approximately $18 billion dollars growing at a Compound Annual Growth Rate (CAGR) 23.01%. At the end of 2022, the software automation industry will be approximately $54.98 billion dollars. Another report by Transparency Market Research estimates that the software automation industry is likely to be at $109.69 billion dollars by the end of 2025. As we can see, software automation is on the rise and has been for a long time. In order to keep up with the current market and current technologies, companies must adopt software automation as a forefront of their commitment to a smoother and safe environment.   Browsers Lab Roadmap  Detailed roadmap shown in white paper and at https://browserslab.com   Browsers Lab Partial Team Navjot B. - Data Engineer LinkedIn Ahmed K - Financial Analyst LinkedIn Navraj K. - Financial Analyst LinkedIn Zainab K. - Risk Enterprise Specialist LinkedIn Roberto L. - Automation Specialist LinkedIn Rafay K. - Software Developer LinkedIn Abigail S. - Software Developer Alex D. - Software Developer  Browsers Lab Allocation  Detailed breakdown of allocations is shown in white paper and at https://browserslab.com  Browsers Lab Frozen Accounts The following Address for the founder has been frozen for 6 months: 0x2F76B8C4e38cCf8F44cF254720182B7636725B1A  Our Commitment to BrowsersLab We are building Browsers Lab because of our need of it. That is the reason why we are committed to going live regardless of the outcome of the ICO campaign. There will be no soft cap because the project will continue and be pushed to production.  Stay Tuned for other news and opportunities. Be the first to get information by subscribing to our Twitter, or any of our social networks.   Browsers Lab PRE-SALE begins March 19th at 9:00 AM EST The minimum contribution for pre-sale is 0.1 Eth or BTC equivalent. The bonus for the pre-sale is 40%  Resource Links How to add BAL tokens to your Wallet  For information on the terms of the pre-sale, please contact investors@browserslab.com  We are a registered business in the state of Maryland, USA.

There are multiple uses of our token. If it has to do with automation, we have a solution for you.
